title: Trying To Make Sense of this Creative World
description: In this week's episode, Ben and Joshua catch up with each other and debrief everything happening in the creative world. We talk about everything from the books we're currently reading, the freelance versus corporate hustle, and what listeners can expect from the podcast in the future.
